channel.title: #@##a challenge for u all! must look!@!#@$$
channel.description:
I am holding a challenge to see who is the best item creator!!! This will show who is truely the best and while i hand out my challenges you can send in your own creations, NOT ITEMS THAT ARE JUST COLOUR CHANGED but ones pretty much from scratch unless it had a base item and is majorly editted!!!
THE FIRST CHALLENGE FOR YOU ALL IS.... DRACONIC ARMOR ... or ... ANGEL / DEVIL ARMOUR with wings, tails, horns ect...
DO NOT POST YOUR ACTUAL ITEM FILE JUST POST PICTURES!!!
GOOD LUCK TO YOU ALL!

item.title: #@##a challenge for u all! must look!@!#@$$
item.dc:creator: @Kindler Kindler
item.description:
@Kindler wrote:

thats my point… how the fuck am i going to copy and paste your gif. files lmao? what im going to put a 2D object on my server? lmao no you got it wrong and hopefully this does bring out the best in people and hopefully alot of rep might come your own way… not that it really matter… we just want to see what you can come up with! this will prove if you really can call yourself a “creator” or a “coder” and most of all by attending the challenge it could be a door to something great on your own personal server…

Still waiting for someone to complete one of the challenges… GOOD LUCK TO ALL OF YOU!
